  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e49e47f4d15346a3256c3fa195747089.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Counter Clash is a fast, fun throwback to classic RTS games build your base, raise your army, and flatten your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/7836f5bac80bd3a38c26c424744ab139.poster.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/7836f5bac80bd3a38c26c424744ab139.webm?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/7836f5bac80bd3a38c26c424744ab139.mp4?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/2967b51c990fd509e660416504866fce.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No tech trees, no spreadsheets just streamlined strategy, chaotic clashes, and factions that include knights, elemental mages, and yes… giants</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e11144ec7e3847a36df99a678cedae18.poster.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e11144ec7e3847a36df99a678cedae18.webm?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e11144ec7e3847a36df99a678cedae18.mp4?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/a0519f28ebd6afc899f8ed29976f59e2.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer a campaign full of grumpy kings and uneasy alliances, or jump into battle mode and see how long you last against an army of elementals. It’s simple to learn, hard to survive, and surprisingly explosive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/cfaa301f396b94be6d4edc4e224e770c.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=298 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Crusade with the Monceaux</strong>, a kingdom of valiant knights and warriors. Their versatile troops, strong siege engines, and holy healing ways are easy to learn but hard to master.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wander with the Fahad</strong>, this nomadic culture harnesses the power of ancient elements. Take to the battlefield with fast, high-damage troops and impactful magics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mechanise with the URA</strong>, a republic of scientists and engineers. What they lack in speed and defence, they compensate with tactical superiority and sheer firepower!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e7878ca37164361963545f6c86ea4a79.poster.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e7878ca37164361963545f6c86ea4a79.webm?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e7878ca37164361963545f6c86ea4a79.mp4?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/88d4d43fe317a949e9beceb2f19af813.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=65 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Campaign Mode</strong>: Guide a paranoid king, a lost shaman, and a grumpy general as they rampage over the lands with ever-changing loyalties, until they are forced into an uneasy alliance to overcome an even greater - and deadlier - foe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle Mode:</strong> Create one-off skirmishes against up to three AI-controlled armies, across multiple maps from simple river crossings to rocky hilltops.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Test Grounds Mode: </strong>Test your tactics against armies of any size! Money is no object in Test Grounds, so build up your - and your enemy's - forces, and let combat commence in battles with endless possibilities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/94b37b7f174691a77aac8e79038f4c33.poster.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/94b37b7f174691a77aac8e79038f4c33.webm?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/94b37b7f174691a77aac8e79038f4c33.mp4?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e49e47f4d15346a3256c3fa195747089.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Counter Clash is a fast, fun throwback to classic RTS games build your base, raise your army, and flatten your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/7836f5bac80bd3a38c26c424744ab139.poster.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/7836f5bac80bd3a38c26c424744ab139.webm?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/7836f5bac80bd3a38c26c424744ab139.mp4?t=1773335312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/2967b51c990fd509e660416504866fce.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No tech trees, no spreadsheets just streamlined strategy, chaotic clashes, and factions that include knights, elemental mages, and yes… giants</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e11144ec7e3847a36df99a678cedae18.poster.avif?t=1773335312\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838160/extras/e11144ec7e3847a36df99a678cedae18.webm?t=1773335312\" type=\"video